{"tid":1924404,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【病毒消失】巴西總統新冠肺炎病毒檢測陰性","createTime":"2020-03-13T16:09:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-13T16:21:47.000Z","uid":52763,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d8d0f336abb1734c3e589b77e80c7f06a6c1481a","tid":1924404,"uid":52763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T16:09:15.000Z","msg":"【巴西總統博索納羅新冠肺炎病毒檢測陰性 】當地時間3月13日，巴西總統博索納羅在其個人社交媒體賬號上發佈消息，稱其新冠肺炎病毒檢測呈陰性。當地時間3月7日-10日，博索納羅對美國進行了訪問，並於7日與美國總統特朗普在佛羅里達州棕櫚灘舉行會晤，在海湖莊園共進晚餐。3月12日，陪同博索納羅一同訪美的巴西總統府媒體事務部門負責人法比奧&middot;瓦恩加滕確診感染新冠肺炎，當天博索納羅及其家人接受了新冠肺炎病毒檢測。當天晚上，博索納羅戴口罩參加了一檔網絡直播節目。目前，代表團其他高級官員的檢測結果尚待官方進一步公佈。雅伊爾&middot;博索納羅自1991年起擔任里約熱內盧州聯邦眾議員，於2018年加入社會自由黨，並在2018年巴西總統選舉中當選為新一任巴西總統。"},{"pid":"6b15c5bce5d8b3d5cac99084bc3345b58c2357b3","tid":1924404,"uid":52763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T16:12:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2215cf39fddb36b4b755624c7ccf1965ad81f29","tid":1924404,"uid":273593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T16:12:06.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">除咗老美之外仲有西班牙<br />\n<br />\n西班牙緊急狀態</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1924394\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1924394</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"eda49889e4b3e5fbf27a9e7f6a5d39607c50475a","tid":1924404,"uid":16061,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T16:12:35.000Z","msg":"其實檢測出錯機會大唔大呢"},{"pid":"55ecdf9e87b5125f49225b491f0d4c6389ad262c","tid":1924404,"uid":64191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T16:13:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/jairbolsonaro/status/1238491455200649219?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fjairbolsonaro%2Fstatus%2F1238491455200649219%3Fs%3D21&d=B95HL5QQ1MLE%2FldfuzA7jwwUjfZSuDKj7BL2vQxkRkA%3D&h=dccfd970\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fjairbolsonaro%2Fstatus%2F1238491455200649219%3Fs%3D21&h=51340da5\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/jairbolsonaro/status/1238491455200649219?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n總統：屌！我冇確診呀！"},{"pid":"3dd95ec7f48f960959a9d1975ad4f3e4d362f8d1","tid":1924404,"uid":9542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T16:13:14.000Z","msg":"佢中唔中已經唔係問題，另一個政客同佢地一齊既已經中左，個程訪問一定出左事<br />\n<br />\nMiami Mayor Suarez tests positive after recent meeting with Senator Rick Scott, Miami-Dade Mayor Carlos Gim&eacute;ne, Donald Trump, &amp; Brazil&rsquo;s President Jair Bolsonaro."},{"pid":"1ed9ab531a350ba785c1739d8717bbd7f52b034c","tid":1924404,"uid":282637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T16:14:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/aTRZB.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FaTRZB.gif&h=5b9f1f3b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"118dd2860d9e70e45dfff1f2b09d38aba2db22c4","tid":1924404,"uid":58958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eda49889e4b3e5fbf27a9e7f6a5d39607c50475a","tid":1924404,"uid":16061,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T16:12:35.000Z","msg":"其實檢測出錯機會大唔大呢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T16:14:31.000Z","msg":"本身隻毒彈出彈入開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78288fdb1a16dc58304367dc5fd5c68d365a883e","tid":1924404,"uid":337076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T16:15:05.000Z","msg":"連燈燈力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b01fdbf72ea5b3155ac7c0ceab83cf18e98cd0d","tid":1924404,"u